content:
Analyze this project brief: 'I want you to make a child story with a teddy bear, it must be something short, around1000 words not more. 
Add some morale to the story and some adventure'.
Generate the required team structure.
Respond ONLY with a JSON matching this exact structure. Use short, unique words for 'team_name' and 'task_name' (e.g., 'Backend', 'UI', 'Database'):
{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "ShortTeamName",
      "role": "Detailed description of their role",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "ShortTaskName", "role": "Their specific role"}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

{
  "managers": [
    {
      "team_name": "Concept",
      "role": "Defines story architecture, adventure sequence, and core moral message.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Outline", "role": "Maps out the adventure plot beats and pacing."},
        {"task_name": "Theme", "role": "Establishes the teddy bear persona and underlying moral lesson."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "team_name": "Drafting",
      "role": "Composes the narrative prose while maintaining child-friendly tone and adventure elements.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Prose", "role": "Writes the main story body focusing on engaging dialogue and action."},
        {"task_name": "Integration", "role": "Seamlessly weaves the moral and adventure threads into the draft."}
      ]
    },
    {
      "team_name": "Review",
      "role": "Validates word count limits, checks moral clarity, and refines stylistic consistency.",
      "employees": [
        {"task_name": "Audit", "role": "Counts words and verifies adherence to the 1000-word maximum constraint."},
        {"task_name": "Polish", "role": "Edits for flow, age-appropriate vocabulary, and emotional resonance."}
      ]
    }
  ]
}
